      "text": "Patrick Sullivan, MD"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Note title']",
      "text": "Progress Note"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Progress note content']",
      "text": "S: Patient reports worsening dyspnea over 3 days, increased sputum production and purulence. Using home nebulizer without relief. Smoked 40 pack-years, quit 2 years ago.\nO: ABG interpretation: pH 7.30, pCO2 55, pO2 58, HCO3 27 \u2014 acute on chronic respiratory acidosis. Oxygen requirements: 3L NC to maintain SpO2 89-92%. RR 24, accessory muscle use noted. CXR with hyperinflation, no consolidation.\nA: Acute COPD exacerbation with respiratory acidosis. Likely infectious trigger given purulent sputum.\nP: Methylprednisolone IV 125mg now, then 60mg q6h. Albuterol nebulizer q4h standing + q2h PRN. Azithromycin for infectious trigger. Steroid plan: IV x 48h then transition to PO prednisone 40mg taper. BIPAP if worsening hypercapnia. ICU transfer if respiratory failure."
    },
    {
      "type": "click",
      "selector": "[data-testid='save-note-button']"
    },
    {
      "type": "wait",
      "milliseconds": 600
    },
    {
      "type": "click",
      "selector": "[data-testid='activity-orders']"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order name']",
      "text": "Methylprednisolone IV"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order category']",
      "text": "MED"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order parameters']",
      "text": "IV, per protocol"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order rationale']",
      "text": "Indicated for COPD exacerbation management"
    },
    {
      "type": "click",
      "selector": "[data-testid='save-order-button']"
    },
    {
      "type": "wait",
      "milliseconds": 600
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order name']",
      "text": "Albuterol nebulizer"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order category']",
      "text": "MED"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order parameters']",
      "text": "Per protocol"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "selector": "[aria-label='Order rationale']",
      "text": "Indicated for COPD exacerbation management"
    },
    {
